text: Korneyevka () is a rural locality (a village) in Starokalkashevsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 101 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Sterlibashevo, 6 km from Stary Kalkash. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Korneyevka, Sterlibashevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
